Package: saferproducts.gov
Title: SaferProducts.gov CPSC Recalls and Penalties Client
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Sean", "B", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "support@scrapeable.com")
Description: Self-contained client for SaferProducts.gov REST API. Search and retrieve CPSC product
